gov.nasa.worldwind.symbology

Interface TacticalCircle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AVList, Highlightable, Movable, Renderable, TacticalGraphic, TacticalPoint
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCircularGraphic, CircularFireSupportArea, CircularPositionArea, PullUpPoint, RoutePoint

    public interface TacticalCircle
extends TacticalPoint
    An interface for circular tactical graphics. This interface provides methods to access the radius of the circle. The radius can also be set using the SymbologyConstants.DISTANCE modifier.
    See Also:
    TacticalGraphicFactory.createCircle(String, gov.nasa.worldwind.geom.Position, double, gov.nasa.worldwind.avlist.AVList)
